mtcars dataset from base R with outliers

Source: R/mtcarsOutliers.R
mtcarsOutliers.Rd

Modified version of mtcars with generated outliers.

Usage

mtcarsOutliers

Format

A data frame with 32 rows and 11 variables:

mpg

double. miles per gallon

cyl

factor number of cylinders

disp

double. displacement (cu.in.)

hp

double. gross horsepower

drat

double. rear axle ratio

wt

double. weight (1000 lbs)

qsec

double. 1/4 mile time

vs

factor engine (0 = v-shaped, 1 = straight)

am

factor transmission (0 = automatic, 1 = manual)

gear

factor number of forward gears

carb

factor number of carburetors

Source

mtcars dataset comes from base R. Outliers are generated using the generateOutliers function from the outForest package.
